---
title: Quick Double Asian Chicken & Veggie Udon Noodles with Oyster Sauce
description: It’s time to work on your slurping game with these udon noodles. You’re going to have to devour the golden crispy chicken and veggies in a rich oyster sauce or even better, slurp it all up on one giant mouthful!
